Texts.Eng: A nasty pirate named Wrexor Nar has been harassing outer-rim systems of late and destabilizing new colonies. Can you please ^orange;kill him^reset; to save countless lives?
Bring the ^green;Stormwarden^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
I can rest easier now, knowing that colony ships carrying human survivors will no longer be attacked by that madman!
